videos.headline: Ionescu blows past everyone for layup and-1
videos.description: Sabrina Ionescu finds space then speeds to the basket and scores a tough layup for a chance at a 3-point play.

videos.headline: Oregon fans applaud Ionescu's 10th career triple-double
videos.description: Sabrina Ionescu hits an easy jumper from the free throw line in the fourth quarter and receives a standing ovation from the crowd as she heads to the bench after notching a triple-double.
